      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owners. The exterior paint still holds a strong shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and well-preserved, with only minor wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. Mechanically, the car is sound and has a solid service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. It offers a great balance of quality and value, presenting very well overall for a pre-owned vehicle.",
