    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained, making it a very reliable option for its next owner. Mechanically, the car is sound; the engine starts up immediately and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. The exterior retains a nice shine, though you will find some minor surface scratches and a few small stone chips on the front bumper consistent with regular highway driving. Inside, the upholstery is clean and free of tears, although there is some light wear on the driver's side seat bolster. All power features, including the air conditioning and infotainment system, are in perfect working order.",
      "price": 34500.0,
