      "description": "Presented in showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface reflects meticulous care, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, smoke-free interior. Mechanically beyond reproach and visually indistinguishable from new, this specimen is suited for the most demanding enthusiast who requires excellence without compromise.",
      "price": 48500.0,
